message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Quantum Effects in Biological Computing: A Computational Investigation of Neural Transport, Coherence, and Reservoir Capacity"
authors:
  - family-names: "Arda"
    given-names: "Celal"
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0009-0006-4563-8325"
