keywords:
  - quantum biology
  - ENAQT
  - reservoir computing
  - Posner molecules
  - ion channels
  - spiking neural networks
  - computational neuroscience
abstract: >-
  Simulation code for five computational experiments investigating
  whether quantum-mechanical effects (tunnelling delays, nuclear-spin
  coherence, environment-assisted quantum transport) can enhance
  neural computation. Includes spiking-network simulations (BRIAN2),
  open-quantum-system dynamics (QuTiP), and echo-state networks.
